* ### on success
* ```
* return "ok"
* ```

* @param  {String[]} args Command arguments.
* @return {Object}
* @throws {Error}

trailingComments.value:
*
* Parse version command response.
*
* ### on success
* ```
* return {
*   branch: "edge",
*   hash  : "9ab4538",
*   date  : "Oct 10 2016 04:09:42",
*   mcu   : "LPC1769",
*   clock : "120MHz"
* }
* ```
* ### on error
* ```
* throw "Unknown version string"
* ```
* @param  {String}   raw  Raw command response string.
* @param  {String[]} args Command arguments.
* @return {Object}
* @throws {Error}
